==Funding a bank==
Funding a bank is possible when the appropriate [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Configuring patches/Economy|patch option]] is enabled. You can only fund banks if population of the town is at least 1200. The cursor will indicate the upper right corner of the 2x1 squares that the bank will occupy. The complete footprint needs to be on top of house(s).

